snippet.title: ABS-CBN'S SHAMELESS ANTI DUTERTE AD

localized.description:
I'm sorry ABS-CBN, but, WHAT THE FUCK IS THIS? Isn't this illegal? Last time I heard, you're not allowed to show an ad that destroys a campaign or public image of  a fellow candidate. 

THEN WHAT THE FUCK IS THIS? PLEASE. GIVE AN EXPLANATION YOU CANCER OF A NETWORK.

Worst part is that you actually used kids in this ad. KIDS. Why?

Bantay Bata, MTRCB; are you really letting this slip through you? Your main objective is the sole protection and rights of these kids and you're letting them get go through unbelievable campaigns like this? Has this stupidity grabbed you by the throat too?

This ad was funded by Trillanes.

UPDATE:
Well according to some sources, Comelec has spoken and they have said that they don't give two shits about what an ad shows or contains, rather they only care about the duration of the ad. Well now, THAT'S fucking brilliant mate! I SO fucking GLAD that our votes are going to be handled by YOU clowns. If you'll excuse me I'll be hiding under a rock.
